[{"text": "Today on What If,", "start": 0.0, "duration": 1.901}, {"text": "we're going to build", "start": 1.901, "duration": 1.102}, {"text": "the highest bridge on planet Earth.", "start": 3.003, "duration": 3.136}, {"text": "Welcome to the Qinghai-Tibet Plateau,", "start": 6.139, "duration": 2.936}, {"text": "the \u201cRoof of the World.\u201d", "start": 9.075, "duration": 2.369}, {"text": "It\u2019s home to the world\u2019s", "start": 11.444, "duration": 1.435}, {"text": "tallest mountain, Mount Everest.", "start": 12.879, "duration": 2.302}, {"text": "But also the longest,", "start": 15.181, "duration": 2.269}, {"text": "deepest canyon on the planet,", "start": 17.45, "duration": 2.57}, {"text": "the Yarlung Zangbo Grand Canyon.", "start": 20.02, "duration": 3.269}, {"text": "This super canyon", "start": 23.289, "duration": 2.002}, {"text": "is 505 km (313 mi) long ", "start": 25.291, "duration": 3.537}, {"text": "and 6 km (3.7 mi) deep.", "start": 28.828, "duration": 2.236}, {"text": "And it\u2019s here ", "start": 31.064, "duration": 1.268}, {"text": "that we\u2019ll be taking on", "start": 32.332, "duration": 1.401}, {"text": "one of the most", "start": 33.733, "duration": 0.768}, {"text": "epic engineering challenges ever.", "start": 34.501, "duration": 2.936}, {"text": "Building a bridge so high", "start": 37.437, "duration": 2.736}, {"text": "it could take your breath away,", "start": 40.173, "duration": 1.969}, {"text": "literally.", "start": 42.142, "duration": 2.636}, {"text": "For inspiration,", "start": 44.778, "duration": 1.101}, {"text": "let\u2019s look at how our project", "start": 45.879, "duration": 1.668}, {"text": "would compare", "start": 47.547, "duration": 0.601}, {"text": "to the world\u2019s current tallest bridge,", "start": 48.148, "duration": 2.736}, {"text": "China\u2019s Beipanjiang bridge.", "start": 50.884, "duration": 3.236}, {"text": "This huge, concrete cable-stayed structure", "start": 54.12, "duration": 3.804}, {"text": "carries people 1,341 m (4,400 ft)", "start": 57.924, "duration": 3.704}, {"text": "across the Beipan River.", "start": 61.628, "duration": 2.169}, {"text": "But even at a dizzying height", "start": 63.797, "duration": 2.369}, {"text": "of 565 m (1,854 ft) above the river,", "start": 66.166, "duration": 4.037}, {"text": "it would find itself", "start": 70.203, "duration": 1.435}, {"text": "in a very distant second place.", "start": 71.638, "duration": 2.803}, {"text": "Our bridge would be", "start": 74.441, "duration": 1.768}, {"text": "over 10 times higher.", "start": 76.209, "duration": 2.236}, {"text": "So let\u2019s get started.", "start": 78.445, "duration": 2.902}, {"text": "Standing face-to-face", "start": 81.347, "duration": 1.769}, {"text": "with the deepest canyon in the world,", "start": 83.116, "duration": 2.436}, {"text": "you\u2019d be so high", "start": 85.552, "duration": 1.268}, {"text": "above the rivers below you", "start": 86.82, "duration": 1.568}, {"text": "that you could stack seven of the world\u2019s", "start": 88.388, "duration": 1.968}, {"text": "tallest skyscraper,", "start": 90.356, "duration": 1.368}, {"text": "the Burj Khalifa, on top of each other.", "start": 91.724, "duration": 3.037}, {"text": "Or the entirety of Mt. Kilimanjaro.", "start": 94.761, "duration": 3.937}, {"text": "But the air you\u2019d be breathing", "start": 98.698, "duration": 2.403}, {"text": "would have less than half", "start": 101.101, "duration": 2.002}, {"text": "of the oxygen available at sea level.", "start": 103.103, "duration": 2.869}, {"text": "While working on this", "start": 105.972, "duration": 1.368}, {"text": "gravity-defying bridge,", "start": 107.34, "duration": 2.136}, {"text": "you could suffer from high-altitude illness.", "start": 109.476, "duration": 3.336}, {"text": "This would make breathing difficult,", "start": 112.812, "duration": 2.403}, {"text": "cause headaches", "start": 115.215, "duration": 0.767}, {"text": "and make you feel light-headed.", "start": 115.982, "duration": 2.736}, {"text": "You and your crew", "start": 118.718, "duration": 1.068}, {"text": "should carry oxygen to be safe.", "start": 119.786, "duration": 2.703}, {"text": "If you got dizzy and fell,", "start": 122.489, "duration": 2.335}, {"text": "you\u2019d drop straight through several", "start": 124.824, "duration": 2.136}, {"text": "different ecosystems.", "start": 126.96, "duration": 2.269}, {"text": "From snowy mountain peaks", "start": 129.229, "duration": 1.801}, {"text": "to temperate coniferous forests", "start": 131.03, "duration": 2.303}, {"text": "to sub-tropical rainforests.", "start": 133.333, "duration": 2.869}, {"text": "All in 35 seconds.", "start": 136.202, "duration": 3.103}, {"text": "Adding to your already", "start": 139.305, "duration": 1.802}, {"text": "full plate of design challenges,", "start": 141.107, "duration": 2.002}, {"text": "you\u2019d be surrounded", "start": 143.109, "duration": 1.468}, {"text": "by tall, dangerous mountain peaks.", "start": 144.577, "duration": 2.436}, {"text": "And your job would be to connect", "start": 147.013, "duration": 2.402}, {"text": "two of these mountains,", "start": 149.415, "duration": 1.669}, {"text": "Namcha Barwa", "start": 151.084, "duration": 2.069}, {"text": "and Gyala.", "start": 153.153, "duration": 2.168}, {"text": "They stand a staggering", "start": 155.321, "duration": 2.069}, {"text": "22 km (13 mi) apart.", "start": 157.39, "duration": 3.003}, {"text": "This would mean that", "start": 160.393, "duration": 1.201}, {"text": "not only would our bridge", "start": 161.594, "duration": 1.368}, {"text": "be 10 times higher", "start": 162.962, "duration": 1.769}, {"text": "than the Beipanjiang,", "start": 164.731, "duration": 1.868}, {"text": "it would also be about 16 times longer.", "start": 166.599, "duration": 4.204}, {"text": "But just like that one,", "start": 170.803, "duration": 2.002}, {"text": " cable-stayed suspension", "start": 172.805, "duration": 1.669}, {"text": "would be the best design option.", "start": 174.474, "duration": 2.235}, {"text": "All you'd need", "start": 176.709, "duration": 1.101}, {"text": "would be massive cables", "start": 177.81, "duration": 1.836}, {"text": "of tightly-braided steel wires.", "start": 179.646, "duration": 2.836}, {"text": "They'd rest on top of towers", "start": 182.482, "duration": 2.235}, {"text": "anchored to either side of the bridge.", "start": 184.717, "duration": 2.803}, {"text": "A suspension bridge like this", "start": 187.52, "duration": 1.735}, {"text": "would also be the best way to go", "start": 189.255, "duration": 1.535}, {"text": "because it would be better", "start": 190.79, "duration": 1.268}, {"text": "at withstanding earthquakes.", "start": 192.058, "duration": 2.503}, {"text": "And the Tibetan Plateau", "start": 194.561, "duration": 1.868}, {"text": "is a region that is highly prone", "start": 196.429, "duration": 2.636}, {"text": "to earthquakes.", "start": 199.065, "duration": 1.535}, {"text": "But that wouldn\u2019t be", "start": 200.6, "duration": 1.234}, {"text": "the only force of nature ", "start": 201.834, "duration": 1.335}, {"text": "you\u2019d have to concern yourself with.", "start": 203.169, "duration": 2.002}, {"text": "You\u2019d also face severe weather.", "start": 205.171, "duration": 2.703}, {"text": "Your crew", "start": 207.874, "duration": 0.967}, {"text": "would need to deal with fog, ", "start": 208.841, "duration": 1.635}, {"text": "rain and freezing temperatures.", "start": 210.476, "duration": 2.77}, {"text": "And then there's the wind.", "start": 213.246, "duration": 1.902}, {"text": "Your design", "start": 215.148, "duration": 1.368}, {"text": "would require the bridge", "start": 216.516, "duration": 1.201}, {"text": "to be as light and as flexible as possible.", "start": 217.717, "duration": 2.669}, {"text": "But you\u2019d need to make sure", "start": 220.386, "duration": 1.502}, {"text": "it remains stable,", "start": 221.888, "duration": 1.668}, {"text": "even in the most extreme winds.", "start": 223.556, "duration": 3.003}, {"text": "One solution would be to build ", "start": 226.559, "duration": 1.669}, {"text": "pendulum-like devices", "start": 228.228, "duration": 1.368}, {"text": "onto each tower", "start": 229.596, "duration": 1.001}, {"text": "to balance any swaying.", "start": 230.597, "duration": 2.135}, {"text": "Or you could construct a stabilizer fin", "start": 232.732, "duration": 3.303}, {"text": "beneath the center of the roadway", "start": 236.035, "duration": 1.402}, {"text": "that would", "start": 237.437, "duration": 0.534}, {"text": "keep movement to a minimum.", "start": 237.971, "duration": 2.202}, {"text": "But enough about the ways", "start": 240.173, "duration": 1.768}, {"text": "weather could affect our bridge.", "start": 241.941, "duration": 2.002}, {"text": "What about the ways", "start": 243.943, "duration": 1.035}, {"text": "our bridge could affect the weather?", "start": 244.978, "duration": 2.469}, {"text": "All of this uber-engineering", "start": 247.447, "duration": 2.169}, {"text": "would be underway in a region", "start": 249.616, "duration": 1.501}, {"text": "that is a diverse habitat", "start": 251.117, "duration": 1.802}, {"text": "for many plants and animals.", "start": 252.919, "duration": 2.069}, {"text": "One of the factors in this", "start": 254.988, "duration": 1.534}, {"text": "is the steep V-shape of the canyon.", "start": 256.522, "duration": 2.77}, {"text": "It helps funnel warm, moist air", "start": 259.292, "duration": 3.003}, {"text": "north from the Indian Ocean", "start": 262.295, "duration": 1.802}, {"text": "up to the plateau.", "start": 264.097, "duration": 1.768}, {"text": "Our bridge would need", "start": 265.865, "duration": 1.568}, {"text": "an entire infrastructure", "start": 267.433, "duration": 1.836}, {"text": "to meet construction demands.", "start": 269.269, "duration": 1.868}, {"text": "Your crew would start by building roads", "start": 271.137, "duration": 2.936}, {"text": "that climb up the mountains.", "start": 274.073, "duration": 1.435}, {"text": "And then, working from both sides", "start": 275.508, "duration": 2.002}, {"text": "at the same time", "start": 277.51, "duration": 0.801}, {"text": "like during the construction ", "start": 278.311, "duration": 1.368}, {"text": "of California's Golden Gate Bridge,", "start": 279.679, "duration": 2.502}, {"text": "you\u2019d bring them together", "start": 282.181, "duration": 1.435}, {"text": "in the center.", "start": 283.616, "duration": 1.235}, {"text": "All this could definitely impact", "start": 284.851, "duration": 2.436}, {"text": "the very important flow of air", "start": 287.287, "duration": 1.801}, {"text": "in the region.", "start": 289.088, "duration": 1.235}, {"text": "And you\u2019d need to make sure", "start": 290.323, "duration": 2.102}, {"text": "that the construction process", "start": 292.425, "duration": 1.702}, {"text": "doesn\u2019t destroy the habitats of wildlife", "start": 294.127, "duration": 2.435}, {"text": "like the Bangladesh tiger,", "start": 296.562, "duration": 1.836}, {"text": "the bear monkey", "start": 298.398, "duration": 0.901}, {"text": "or the giant boa constrictor.", "start": 299.299, "duration": 2.335}, {"text": "Would it be worth it?", "start": 301.634, "duration": 2.269}, {"text": "And is there any way to calculate ", "start": 303.903, "duration": 2.636}, {"text": "the final price tag ", "start": 306.539, "duration": 1.468}, {"text": "for a project so huge", "start": 308.007, "duration": 1.869}, {"text": "and with so many challenges?", "start": 309.876, "duration": 2.169}, {"text": "Well, given that this is", "start": 312.045, "duration": 1.701}, {"text": " 16 times bigger than the Beipanjiang,", "start": 313.746, "duration": 3.27}, {"text": "it could cost upward of $2 billion,", "start": 317.016, "duration": 4.571}, {"text": "at the very least.", "start": 321.587, "duration": 1.836}, {"text": "But that would be pretty cheap", "start": 323.423, "duration": 2.836}, {"text": "compared to an even more", "start": 326.259, "duration": 1.701}, {"text": "daring feat of engineering,", "start": 327.96, "duration": 1.736}, {"text": "a highway in space.", "start": 329.696, "duration": 2.769}, {"text": "But that\u2019s a story for another WHAT IF.", "start": 332.465, "duration": 7.274}]